# Local-only eval fixtures — REAL PATIENT TRANSCRIPTS + NOTES (PHI).
# Never commit. Used as regression cases for prompt changes; live only on
# Dr. Hobbs's machine.
#
# Real PHI fixture dirs are date-prefixed (YYYY-MM-DD-*) and remain ignored.
# Synthetic fixture dirs must be prefixed `synthetic-` and are tracked, since
# they contain no real patient data. Runner harnesses + README are tracked.
# Use `eval-fixtures/*` (not `eval-fixtures/`) so negations can re-include
# specific children — git won't recurse into a fully-ignored directory.
eval-fixtures/*
!eval-fixtures/synthetic-*/
!eval-fixtures/synthetic-*/**
!eval-fixtures/run_eval.py
!eval-fixtures/run_sibling_eval.py
!eval-fixtures/README.md
eval-fixtures/__pycache__/

